{"tid":815372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有冇7-11呀? ] 【車Cam直擊】石澳道電單車撼貨車 鐵騎士不治","createTime":"2018-09-12T04:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T17:44:24.000Z","uid":160094,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0df7a7aa8dea2b61edbea3c206fca9ee7c93970","tid":815372,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jlYA20sa_Cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjlYA20sa_Cs&d=0ae027bs3124tcF0V6cgnE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=27555d5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jlYA20sa_Cs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港島石澳道本月內發生第二宗致命車禍，凌晨零時25分，一名姓伍(37歲)鐵騎士，駕駛一輛英國TRIUMPH Thruxton 900cc仿古電單車，沿石澳道往石澳方向行駛，至爛泥灣一個左彎，失控越過對面線，與一輛運載道具密斗貨車相撞，貨車司機閃避扭軚撞向山邊。電單車車頭懾入貨車車底，鐵騎士重創昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n尾隨TRIUMPH另一輛川崎ZX 1000，姓孫27歲司機緊急煞車亦告墮地，他與姓陳46歲貨車司機同告受傷，幸傷勢並不嚴重。救護員將三名傷者送院，TRIUMPH姓伍司機搶救證實不治。據稱，死者是一名設計師。事後有10多名親友到醫院了解情況，有親友聞悉死訊傷心痛哭，一名女親友不適要坐輪椅及旁人安慰。警方調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n據往柴灣方向一輛汽車車Cam顯示，約有六輛電單車沿石澳道入石澳，出事TRIUMPH在車隊之後，失事撞到貨車後，後面的川崎閃避亦告翻側，剷向對面行車線，司機倒地能夠自行起來。汽車車Cam拍攝事發一刻時，司機嘩一聲叫了出來。<br />\n案件交港島總區交通意外調查隊跟進，警方指任何人如目睹意外發生或有資料提供，請致電3660 6800與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n本月2日中午，一輛私家車沿石澳道往大浪灣方向行駛，近石澳泳灘一個落斜左彎，失控越過對面線，與一輛駛至的新巴9號線巴士相撞，姓黎62歲私家車司機重傷被困，送院搶救不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180912&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58671187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180912%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58671187&d=0ae027bs3124tcF0V6cgnE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8579c9d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180912%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58671187&h=948e0df2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180912&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58671187</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好口渴呀 買樽水飲下 有冇7-11呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf11ef4f7745609166e1b20a61b76eec544061af","tid":815372,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"留言等睇有人講架貨車見有人賽梗車，就應該一早停車唔好行啦。"},{"pid":"dbbc3e0d42d665693b83976e401fdf2a8fbcb561","tid":815372,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07097300a8c301d9f00ac3335721f613e7890af1","tid":815372,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"貨車司機好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bef45d1b031447f05673f9202169bad6313760c","tid":815372,"uid":16624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"阿婆鬧死"},{"pid":"71bfa6b15a9e990e82b294a60d3e70f46ea43c92","tid":815372,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"抵仆街 怨得邊個<br />\n貨車司機最慘"},{"pid":"f8de082308cd54ce595838e1337eadb3301e1fd9","tid":815372,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf11ef4f7745609166e1b20a61b76eec544061af","tid":815372,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"留言等睇有人講架貨車見有人賽梗車，就應該一早停車唔好行啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"停車咪一樣撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd3628077adf120ad7a1ae2cd7cfb86ba4cbff3","tid":815372,"uid":160094,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bef45d1b031447f05673f9202169bad6313760c","tid":815372,"uid":16624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"阿婆鬧死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"阿婆知道鬧梗架 而家點整 <br />\n俾佢知道車都冇得渣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325e9701d20009d86aab7d7ec9b8c1603b25776b","ti